{"tid":993094,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手養貓一問","createTime":"2019-01-23T16:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T16:46:03.000Z","uid":59410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d41ac9d4354f2c81b57c4872c455a93295b1d15e","tid":993094,"uid":59410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"第一次養貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎左一個星期 8個月大英短仔<br />\n英短仔成日明明無屎尿屙<br />\n但係就成日走入貓砂盆到係咁摷<br />\n到底係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋隻貓仔成日用後腳R兩邊耳仔<br />\n本身無為意 但係啱啱發覺抓到損鬼左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係因為有耳屎定咩原因 係咪要買野幫佢清耳仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaOE3Cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaOE3Cf.png&h=af143930&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvFW5QC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvFW5QC.png&h=ceaf58e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmAzSvF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmAzSvF.png&h=677da2f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f640a1b4f22e77d9a4cc4447ecc17e166117a23","tid":993094,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},{"pid":"4d06f8a2a62dd91a093ee106746a8c19346852e9","tid":993094,"uid":59410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f640a1b4f22e77d9a4cc4447ecc17e166117a23","tid":993094,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f393ae37df17f341331ceb799e279526806f1cbe","tid":993094,"uid":233014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"首先係無屎尿入砂盆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依樣野係正常㗎 因為佢地想入去留番自己嘅氣味喺入面<br />\n我每次換完砂毛釘都會入去搞下先<br />\n至於耳仔<br />\n可能會有耳蟎！如果真係有就要去獸醫嗰到買藥<br />\n平時都要幫佢抹耳仔<br />\n寵物店會有一枝枝專抹耳仔嘅藥水，抹眼仔嘅都有<br />\n除左買藥水再買啲綿花<br />\n至於點抹可以上網睇片 我依度講都唔清楚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果抹完都仲成日R 真係要睇下醫生"}]}